These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
City: edinburgh, hannover
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| City         | hannover | edinburgh |
| Flower     | tulip | amaryllis    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, d&b
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, fishing
1. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Music-Genre           | d&b         | country     |
| Hobby     | dancing   | fishing    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: german, egyptian
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, blue
1. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the german is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Nationality    | egyptian     | german |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Color   | mauve         | blue    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, pall-mall
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, cooking
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, rowing
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Cigar          | pall-mall   | aristoff  |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking     |
| Sport   | climbing  | rowing         |

