There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, cabbage
1. the person eating cabbage is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the electrician is the dutch##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
